%TITLE Help on %w%lautomatic character deletion%x
If you don't connect for some time, your character may be %r%lautomatically deleted%x by %@%n.  If you don't want this to happen, please make sure you connect regularly.  The allowed times are detailed when you disconnect from the game (A period of %y%l200 days%x is usually allowed for a Builder, %y%l100 days%x for a Mortal and %y%l1 month%x for 'newbies' (Characters with less than %c%l1 day%x total connect time.))

If you are going to be away from the Internet for longer than these times, and will be returning afterwards, please ask a member of Admin to set your %y%l%(PERMANENT%)%x flag, which will prevent your character from being automatically destroyed.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<permanent flag%>%x', '%g%l%<@maintenance%>%x' and '%g%l%<@admin%>%x'.

