Returns the time and date when the longest connect time of the character %y%l<NAME>%x occurred, in either the %c%lEPOCH%x (See '%g%l%<epoch%>%x') or %c%lLONGDATE%x (See '%g%l%<longdate%>%x') date/time format (If the date/time format is not specified, %c%lEPOCH%x will be assumed.)

