When you're the controller of a character, you can '%g%l%(@force%)%x' (See '%g%l%<@force%>%x') them to do things and examine/modify/destroy most of the objects which belong to them.

For any testing of compound commands/areas/building work you must use a hirable puppet from the %y%lPuppet Bank%x (Type '%g%lpuppet%x' to access this.)

