If you're an %y%lApprentice Wizard/%yDruid%x or above, you can use '%g%l@quota initialise%x' to re-initialise the Building Quota in use for all characters in the database (%c%lNOTE:  %xThis is done on start-up, so there should be no need for you to use this command.)
