Sets (Or resets, if %y%l<DESCRIPTION>%x is omitted) an alternative contents string for a room or thing, which will be displayed instead of the standard '%y%l%uContents:%x' when the room/thing has visible contents and is looked at.

%c%l%8NOTE:  %xThe maximum length for a contents string is %c%l79 characters%x.


%c%l%$Examples:
