%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%l@maintenance bbs|characters|mail|objects|requests%]%x

This command allows %m%lDeities%x and the %m%lSupreme Being%x to manually start %c%lBBS%x, %c%lcharacter%x, %c%lmail%x, %c%lobject%x or %c%lnew character request queue%x maintenance.

%4%r%l*  %xBBS maintenance removes messages which haven't been read for the time set in topics which have a time limit.
%4%y%l*  %xCharacter maintenance destroys unused characters in the database.
%4%r%l*  %xMail maintenance deletes mail which hasn't been read for %c%l50 days%x or more.
%4%y%l*  %xObject maintenance destroys unused objects and junked objects in the database.
