%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%l@mass <OBJECT> = <VALUE>|inherit|infinity%]%x

Sets the mass of %y%l<OBJECT>%x to %y%l<VALUE>%x kilograms.  If '%y%linherit%x' is specified for %y%l<VALUE>%x, %y%l<OBJECT>%x's mass will be inherited from its parent object.

%y%lApprentice Wizards/%yDruids%x and above may also set the mass of an object to '%y%linfinity%x'.
