%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%l@set me|*<NAME> = FEMALE
        @set me|*<NAME> = !FEMALE%]%x

This flag represents the gender of a character.  You can set your gender by typing '%g%l%(@set%) me = male%x', '%g%l%(@set%) me = female%x' or '%g%l%(@set%) me = neuter%x'.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<male flag%>%x', '%g%l%<neuter flag%>%x' and '%g%l%<@set%>%x'.

