Sets the volume of %y%l<OBJECT>%x to %y%l<VALUE>%x litres (There are %c%l10 litres%x to a %c%lcubic metre%x.)  If '%y%linherit%x' is specified for %y%l<VALUE>%x, %y%l<OBJECT>%x's volume will be inherited from its parent object.

%y%lApprentice Wizards/%yDruids%x and above may also set the volume of an object to '%y%linfinity%x'.
