%~%c~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
%4%r%l*  %xWelcoming and giving general assistance to new users (See '%g%l%<welcome%>%x' and '%g%l%<assist%>%x'.)
%4%y%l*  %xLearning how to deal with problem users.
%4%r%l*  %xLearning how to check for and deal with duplicate users.
%4%y%l*  %xAsking %cDruids%x or %gElder Druids%x about anything they are unsure about.

%PAGE

%c%l%$Summary of Druid and Elder Druid duties:
%~%c~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
%4%r%l*  %xWelcoming and giving assistance to new users (See '%g%l%<welcome%>%x' and '%g%l%<assist%>%x'.)
%4%y%l*  %xDealing with abusive, offensive and problem users.
%4%r%l*  %xDealing with and resolving disputes between users and/or Admin.
%4%y%l*  %xChecking for and dealing with offensive or abusive material built or posted to the BBS (See '%g%l%<bbs%>%x') by users.
%4%r%l*  %xDealing with any building problems which are within scope of knowledge, refering to %c%lWizard%x administration (See '%g%l%<wizards%>%x') where necessary.
%4%y%l*  %xChecking for and dealing with any Admin. power abuse.
