The '%g%lfremove%x' command is used to either remove a friend from your friends list, or forcibly remove yourself from another character's friends list (Providing they haven't set/reset additional friend flags on you (See '%g%l%<fset%>%x')), e.g:  '%g%lfremove fred bloggs%x' will remove the user '%y%lFred Bloggs%x' from your friends list, %c%lAND/OR%x remove you from their friends list (If you're on it.)

%c%lNOTE:  %xThe character you'd like to remove doesn't have to be connected.
