%TOPIC emergencycommandlogging
%TITLE Help on '%w%lemergency%x'
%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%lemergency <NAME> = <REASON>%]%x

Sooner or later, you'll probably come across a really annoying character, who spends their time doing nothing else other than abusing or harassing you and other characters.

%r%lIf you come across a character like this, you can use the '%y%lemergency%r%l' command to get something done about it...%x

Type '%g%lemergency%x' followed by the %c%lname of the character%x and your %c%lreason%x, e.g:  '%g%lemergency fred = He is using really offensive language%x' (%c%lPLEASE NOTE:  %xThe word '%g%lemergency%x' must be typed in %c%lFULL%x.)

All commands typed by the user will be logged to '%y%lEmergency%x' log file for the next %c%l5 minutes%x, and details of the character and your reason for using '%g%lemergency%x' will be sent to all connected administrators, so that they can take appropriate action to sort the problem out.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<enemy friend flag%>%x' and '%g%l%<complain%>%x'.

