If %y%l<PAGE NO>%x is specified, the list of comments will be split up into pages and the page number specified will be displayed, e.g:  '%g%lsession 1%x', '%g%lsession 2%x', etc.

%y%lApprentice Wizards/%yDruids%x and above may reset unsuitable session titles or change the current session before the %c%l15 minute%x time period by using the '%g%lsession reset [<TITLE>]%x' command.  They may also change unsuitable session comments by typing '%g%lsession reset = <NAME>%x', where %y%l<NAME>%x is the name of the character who has set an unsuitable session comment.
