If %y%l<NAME>%x is specified, just that one character is listed.  If one or more flags (Separated by spaces) are specified instead of %y%l<NAME>%x, only characters with those flags are listed, e.g:  '%g%llwho admin%x', '%g%llwho mortals%x', '%g%llwho haven quiet%x', etc.
