If you're inside a container or vehicle which can be entered, you can look out of the container/vehicle (I.e:  Look at its current location) by typing '%g%llook outside%x'.  If you're inside a container, it must be open to look out of it (If it's closed, you can open it by typing '%g%l%(open%) here%x' (See '%g%l%<open%>%x'.))  You can also look out of non-%y%l%(OPAQUE%)%x containers (See '%g%l%<opaque flag%>%x'.)

