%TITLE Help on %@%n Mail System
%@%n Mail System is an easy to use internal mailing system that can be used to mail messages to other characters/friends (Regardless of whether they're connected or not.)  Using it is simple...

To mail a message to someone, simply type '%g%lmail <NAME>%x'.  Type your message, pressing %c%lRETURN%x after each line.  Once you've finished, type '%g%l%(.view%)%x' to check it and then '%g%l%(.save%)%x' to save your changes and mail your message (If you're happy with it.)  Otherwise, type '%g%l%(.abort%) = yes%x' to abandon your message (And not mail it.)

To list the latest messages in your mailbox, type '%g%lmail%x'.  If you're really popular and have lots of mail, you can list your first page of messages by typing '%g%lmail page 1%x', the second by typing '%g%lmail page 2%x', and so on.

To read a message that someone's mailed to you, type '%g%lmail read = <NUMBER>%x'.

%PAGE
To see how much mail you have, and how much of it is unread at a glance, type '%g%lmail update%x'.

To delete an item of mail you no longer want, type '%g%lmail delete = <NUMBER>%x'.  You can delete all of your mail by typing '%g%lmail delete = all%x'.

If you need any help, '%g%l%(page%)%x' or mail an %y%lApprentice Wizard/%yDruid%x or above.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<bbs%>%x', '%g%l%<mail flag%>%x' and '%g%l%<mail friend flag%>%x'.

