The above two commands ('%g%ltf%x' and '%g%lpf%x') are aliases for the commands '%g%l%(tell%) %(friends%) <MESSAGE>%x' and '%g%l%(page%) %(friends%) <MESSAGE>%x' respectively.  They are provided for convenience (And are easier/quicker to type too.)
<-SEPARATOR->
