%TOPIC blocktells
%TOPIC pageblocking
%TOPIC tellblocking
%TITLE Help on blocking pages and tells from other characters
You can stop a particular character from being able to page/tell messages to you by adding them to your friends list (By typing '%g%l%(fadd%) <NAME>%x') and then typing '%g%l%(fset%) <NAME> = !pagetell%x'.  You can even make them one of your enemies by typing '%g%l%(fset%) <NAME> = enemy%x'.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<page%>%x', '%g%l%<tell%>%x', '%g%l%<friends%>%x', '%g%l%<fset%>%x' and '%g%l%<.message%>%x'.

