%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%lQUIT%]%x

Makes you log out and leave %@%n.  This command %c%lMUST%x be typed in capitals.

'%g%lQUIT%x' can be used at any time, even if you haven't created or connected a character, however, it CAN'T be used from within a compound command.

