%TITLE Help on '%w%lprofile%x'
%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%lprofile [<NAME>] [= secret]%]%x

Every character on %@%n has a profile.  You can use your profile to set detailed information about yourself, which other users can view (By using the '%g%lprofile%x' command) to find out more about you.

The '%g%lprofile%x' command displays detailed information about the character %y%l<NAME>%x (Or yourself, if %y%l<NAME>%x isn't specified.)  You can set your own profile by using the '%g%l%(@profile%)%x' command (See '%g%l%<@profile%>%x'.)

If the second parameter ('%y%l= secret%x') is specified, the user's '%y%l.profile%x' compound command (If they have one (See '%g%l%<.profile%>%x')) will not be executed.
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<@profile%>%x', '%g%l%<scan%>%x', '%g%l%<look%>%x', '%g%l%<inventory%>%x', '%g%l%<examine%>%x' and '%g%l%<.profile%>%x'.

%COMMENT --------------------------------------------------------------------->

%TOPIC scores
%TOPIC points
%TOPIC scoring
%TITLE Help on '%w%lscore%x'
%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%lscore%]%x

Displays how much Building Quota you have in use and your present Building Quota limit, your current score and how much credit (Money) you have.

You can rank users by typing '%g%l%<@rank%>%x' (See '%g%l%<@rank%>%x') followed by one of the following:  %y%lScore%x, %y%lCredit%x, %y%lBalance%x, %y%lQuotalimit%x (Admin. only).
<-SEPARATOR->
Also, see '%g%l%<scan%>%x', '%g%l%<profile%>%x', '%g%l%<inventory%>%x' and '%g%l%<@rank%>%x'.

