%TITLE Help on '%w%lscreenconfig%x'
%[%c%lUSAGE:  %g%lscreenconfig%]%x

Asks you a number of questions designed to help you set up %@%n to suit your computer/terminal.  If you connect from a different computer/terminal than the one you used when you first connected, you may find you need to run through the '%g%lscreenconfig%x' questions again.


%c%l%$'%w%l%$screenconfig%c%l%$' does the following...%x
%~%c~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
%4%r%l*  %xDetermines whether your computer/terminal supports ANSI colour.  (Also determines whether 8 or 16 colour ANSI should be used.)
